@startuml
title Activity Diagram: Generate Features from SRS (AI)

|User|
start
:Navigate to project features page;
:Click "Generate Features with AI" button;

|System|
:Check if SRS document exists;
if (SRS document exists?) then (no)
  |User|
  :Show error: "Please upload SRS document first";
  stop
else (yes)
  |System|
  :Retrieve relevant context chunks\nfrom project_vectors;
  :Generate features using LLM\n(based on SRS context);
  :Parse AI response (JSON);
  if (Valid features generated?) then (no)
    |User|
    :Show error: "Failed to generate features";
    stop
  else (yes)
    |System|
    :Save features to MongoDB;
    :Store feature embeddings in Supabase;
    |User|
    :Display generated features;
    :Option to edit/delete features;
    :Option to generate test cases;
    stop
  endif
endif

@enduml

